text: Cuitlatec or Cuitlatec may refer to: * Cuitlatec people, a historic ethnic group of Guerrero, Mexico * Cuitlatec language, the extinct language isolate formerly spoken by them == See also == * Cuicatecs, an ethnic group of Oaxaca, Mexico * Cuicatec language, the Oto-Manguean language spoken by them
title: Cuitlatec
